product_description: A healthy mix of four wholesome grains  rolled into thin chips for that delightful nutty flavor.
It could be the original crunch that makes it everybody's favorite.
Melt in your mouth,light and puffy curls coated in delicious cheese flavor.
A huge variety of crisps,chips,crackers and popcorn is available in exciting flavors,from the simple salted to snacks flavored with cheese,spices and more.
Made with real cheese, these crispy,crunchy crisps are perfect for satisfying your cheesy cravings.
